divs: Sighting DetailsI was at work (working nights)unloading one of our paint booths i was looking at the sky (which i do from time to time) when i noticed this circle object in the sky. I thought it was a satellite moving across the sky so i kept my eye on it for about 10 secs when out of no where it took off so fast it turned into a flash of blueish green and then just dissapeared into the sky.
